{"tid":1447368,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分享策略：政界猛人揭林鄭底牌 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:58:12.000Z","uid":275524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0703994def1780664bdfedc1b4334976f6f6c578","tid":1447368,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:50:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20190811/20746692?fbclid=IwAR16nYCecz_poRGcpIdp3Acs46zI0d2k_7SiaAwVzcu7onLLGizyDB732eM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190811%2F20746692%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR16nYCecz_poRGcpIdp3Acs46zI0d2k_7SiaAwVzcu7onLLGizyDB732eM&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTIGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=3f494282\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190811%2F20746692%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR16nYCecz_poRGcpIdp3Acs46zI0d2k_7SiaAwVzcu7onLLGizyDB732eM&h=f405e58f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20190811/20746692?fbclid=IwAR16nYCecz_poRGcpIdp3Acs46zI0d2k_7SiaAwVzcu7onLLGizyDB732eM</a> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>政府一味拖，呢段時間示威者有咩要注意？他說：「政府知香港人怕暴力怕亂，又金魚記憶，齋拖已經成功一半㗎啦。只要打多幾次大交，大家就唔知道邊個啱邊個錯，最後示威者嘅支持就慢慢流失。依家連黑社會都出埋，呢班人冇道德底線，開片係其次，最陰毒係佢可以冒充示威者，抹黑年輕人&hellip;&hellip;」X先生說的抹黑方法，我不便公開，但不難猜到。相比起黑警明刀明槍，更可怕的是黑社會陰招。我現在早一步寫出來，希望將來一般市民評論示威者時，務必運用批判思考，想想是否有人在「移屍嫁禍」。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n有什麼是抗爭者可做，但還未做的事？X先生說：「第一，我講多次，就係日日打721呢個死穴，因為林鄭同警方依家完全冇得拆。第二，將民建聯同黑警綑綁，要佢哋永不分離。中央撐警，建制派一定要歸隊，冇可能割席。好多人冇留意到北京撐警，其實係一把雙刃劍，好處係穩定軍心，防止警察叛變，壞處係會累死建制派。大家點解唔日日問吓民建聯啲區議員同立法會議員，『你撐唔撐警』、『覺唔覺得警察濫用暴力』呢？記住問是非題，一係yes，一係no，咪畀位佢遊花園呀。</blockquote> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣方向，可參考：<br />\n1. 721721721721721721721721721721 <br />\n2. 今日冒充示威者，抹黑年輕人個幾個黑衣人<br />\n3. 唔好移屍嫁禍，重點係5大訴求，記住敵人不係狗，係林鄭<br />\n4. 將民建聯同黑警綑綁，未來選舉大清洗 </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bebd54d0d509afb84cd2681b08e7f9679785cb13","tid":1447368,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}